        An imperfect Python ECS
        
        * Free software: BSD license
        * Documentation: http://rui.rtfd.org.
        
        Features
        --------
        
        * A simple Python Entity Component System
        * Unoptimized
        * Favors World based access, eschews Managers (Artemis, which inspired this, uses both)
        
        
        
        
